name: AC
description: Activity. Letter code of the activity of the vessel.

name: AD
description: The name of the sender (ex. PAN for Panama, FR for France).

name: AE
description: Area of Entry. Division Entering into.

name: AF
description: Assigned inspectors. Identification of the inspector; 3-Alpha country code and number, in pairs as needed.

name: AU
description: Authentication. Code to authenticate the report or message used for flag state domestic purposes.

name: BA
description: Bait. Type of bait.

name: BD
description: Block Date. UTC time for the data in the block.

name: BE
description: Beam length (Gear). Beam length in meters.

name: BT
description: Block Time. UTC time for the data in the block.

name: BD
description: Block Date. UTC time for the data in the block.

name: TM
description: The transmission method used.

name: NA
description: Name of the vessel

name: IR
description: Unique vessel number attributed by the flag-State

name: RC
description: International Radio Call Sign (IRCS) of the observed/sighted vessel

name: XR
description: Side (hull) number of registration of the vessel

name: DA
description: Date of reported event (year, month, day in UTC)

name: TI
description: Time of reported event (hour, minute in UTC)

name: LT
description: Latitude expressed in degrees and decimals (WGS-84)

name: LG
description: Longitude expressed in degrees and decimals (WGS-84)

name: SP
description: The speed of the vessel.

name: CO
description: The course of the vessel.

name: FS
description: The flag of the vessel.

name: IM
description: IMO ship identification number.

name: ID
description: ID number for the transmitter/platform.

name: SQ
description: Serial number of the message/report as transmitted by the vessel (annual count).
